Package exceptions

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    BoyNotCommitted
    This class defines exception if you are trying to access committed attributes of boy which is not committed
    GirlAlreadyCommitted
    This class defines exception which is thrown if trying to allocate boy to a girl who is already committed
    GirlBudgetFulfilled
    This class defines exception which is thrown if girl's maintenance budget is fulfilled yet boy keeps on adding gifts to basket
    GirlNotCommitted
    This class defines exception which is thrown if Girl is not committed
    InvalidBoyDetail
    This class defines exception which is thrown if no boy exist at the index which is trying to be accessed
    InvalidCoupleNumber
    This class defines exception which is thrown if trying to access no of couples greater than present or less than 0
    InvalidGift
    This class defines exception which is thrown if trying to access gift which is yet not been defined
    InvalidGirlType
    This class defines error which is thrown if no girl type has not been assigned yet
    NoBoyTypeFound
    This class defines exception which is thrown if the boy has not been allocated any type and thus do not have any details
    NoCoupleFoundAtIndex
    This class defines exception which is thrown if someone trying to access couple index at which no valid couple exist.
    NoEligibleBfFoundException
    This class defines exception which is thrown if no boy fulfills all requirements to be boyfriend of girl and thus no bf could be found for her
    NoGiftTypeFound
    This class defines exception which is thrown if no gift type has yet been allocated to gift and thus has no details
